+COMMAND ===>_ZCMD                                            @ZTIME+on@
}                            General Information (6)                   @
}
+ The Keep Option
} If JOB Card Generation is entered with the command\JOBC K}then an atte
} made to retrieve information from a current JOB Card, providing it sta
} line one of the data being edited.  No attempt is made to delete your
} Card.  You must do this yourself.
}
} The information is retrieved before the JOB Card panel is displayed, a
} so will be displayed on the panel.  It will over-ride any data kept in
} profile dataset (see later Help panel).  The following data is sought:
}   Last five letters of Jobname.
}   Account code and application code.
}   Programmer's Name field (job description).
}   Job class, Message class and Region size.
}
} The Keep option is easily confused and will then give up (a message ma
} displayed, and some data may have been retrieved).
}
                        +For more information press%ENTER}
